					<div class="bio">
						<h4>Judson Bergman</h4>
												<p>Judson Bergman, <em>Image</em>’s design associate, has worked as a designer, college professor, prison minister, youth pastor, and in construction. He has studied at Yale, Harvard, Wheaton, and Union Theological Seminary. He lives with his wife, Ally, in Brooklyn and Ann Arbor.</p>
